OL,3,CMenai Bridge to partially reopen after
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,FThe Menai Suspension Bridge will
OL,7,Fpartially reopen after it was closed
OL,8,Fdue to safety concerns, the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment has announced.
OL,11,FThe sudden closure of the Anglesey
OL,12,Flink came into force over the weekend
OL,13,Fafter a recent investigation revealed
OL,14,Fthat bolts on beams under the bridge
OL,15,Fneed to be replaced.
OL,17,FThere had initially been a weight
OL,18,Flimit imposed but the UK Highways
OL,19,FAgency said they faced difficulties in
OL,20,Fenforcing restrictions.
