OL,3,CMenai Bridge to partially reopen after
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, October 7, the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment announced a partial and
OL,8,Frestricted reopening of the bridge to
OL,9,Fcars, motorcyclists and pedestrians.
OL,11,FThe partial reopening will be in place
OL,12,Ffrom 7am to 7pm with a full closure
OL,13,Fovernight.
OL,15,FDuring the hours of operation, the
OL,16,Fbridge will be limited to vehicles up
OL,17,Fto a 3-tonne weight limit, with
OL,18,Ftraffic management and a single flow
OL,19,Fof traffic off the island in the
OL,20,Fmorning and onto the island in the
OL,21,Fafternoon.
