OL,3,CMenai Bridge to partially reopen after
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,FCyclists will be expected to dismount
OL,7,Fwhen on the bridge and use the
OL,8,Fpedestrian footway. Emergency access
OL,9,Farrangements for ambulances not able
OL,10,Fto cross the Britannia Bridge will be
OL,11,Fin place.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government says discussions
OL,14,Fare ongoing with UK Highways A55 DBFO
OL,15,FLtd and North Wales Police and
OL,16,Fconfirmation of timescales and
OL,17,Fenforcement will be provided as soon
OL,18,Fas a plan is fully agreed.
